        {
            "title": "1個月HIBOR跌至1.29厘 創逾兩年半低",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"1個月HIBOR跌至1.29厘 創逾兩年半低\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/a0baa2cebf6592b9f660fa09dba54593/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250516/_2025051612114339856.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">1個月HIBOR跌至1.29厘 創逾兩年半低</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>港元同業拆息（HIBOR）普遍向上，其中與樓按相關的1個月拆息報1.29798厘，較前一個交易日的1.35083厘跌5.29點子，創1個月新低，亦是自2022年8月2日後最低，當日報1.28786厘。\n\n</p>\n<p>香港銀行公會資料顯示，多數期限的拆息均錄得上升，而1星期HIBOR則跌2.44點子至0.48833厘，至於隔夜HIBOR升0.45點子至0.06196厘。\n\n</p>\n<p>較長期拆息方面，反映銀行資金成本的3個月HIBOR升7.66點子至2.19619厘；6個月HIBOR升13.23點子至2.79226厘；12個月期HIBOR升10.7點子至3.25107厘。\n\n</p>\n<p>相關新聞：\n\n</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/investment/3455852/\">銀行員工被裁 失10成按揭影響大 恐補差價兼捱貴息 專家：轉按要3個月入息</a><br/>\n \n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2069222/即時-財經-1個月HIBOR跌至1-29厘-創逾兩年半低",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-16 12:22:00",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "北角電氣道超市門外被淋白油  警緝歹徒",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"地上有大灘白油。林思明攝\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/1847c9dd025b5a78e7f03d69934c76fc/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250516/_2025051612022754185.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">地上有大灘白油。林思明攝</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>今（16日）晨7時許，北角電氣道一間超市門外被潑淋白油，面積約5米乘5米，警員接報到場，翻查閉路電視追查疑犯下落及犯案過程，列刑毀案跟進，暫未有人被捕。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4251546/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"地上有大灘白油。林思明攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/fd359097dceee0fe0f4e342a354858e0/2025-05/01_1_17.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        地上有大灘白油。林思明攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4251547/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"地上有大灘白油。林思明攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4cdd7a729dbb9645e8aaac235907b1ab/2025-05/03_1_4.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        地上有大灘白油。林思明攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
